===================
cryptography.branca
===================

cryptography.branca is a thin layer on top of cryptography.fernet_ that
uses passwords and not keys as secret. The key is derived from the
password with a key derivation function.

To install the package use pip::

   $ pip install --user cryptography.branca

To run the tests::

   $ python -m unittest test_branca


.. _cryptography.fernet: https://cryptography.io/en/latest/fernet/

